🏥 OpenEnv Healthcare: RL Patient Stabilization
A Reinforcement Learning (RL) system designed to stabilize ICU patients by managing heart rate, oxygen saturation, and medication toxicity. This project implements the OpenEnv 2026 modular standard for healthcare AI.

🚀 Performance Summary
Through an automated clinical audit, the agent demonstrated a significant intelligence leap:

Random Baseline Score: 0.25 (Initial "NoneType" state)

Trained Agent Score: 0.82 (Stabilized)

