The system is built on four modular layers to ensure medical data integrity and reproducibility:

Environment (openenv_healthcare.py): A custom Gymnasium environment simulating an ICU unit with physics-based vital sign drift.

Data Pipeline (data_pipeline.py): An ingestion layer that maps real-world patients.csv data into the simulation.

Agent Logic (master_audit.py): Utilizes Stable Baselines3 (PPO) to train a "Doctor AI" through 50,000 trial-and-error iterations.

